U . S . Stockpile sells tin in long - term contract . The U . S . Defense National Stockpile Center said it sold 5 , 000 tonnes of surplus longhorn tin to Considar Inc of New York at a provisional fair market value in excess of $ 31 million . The agency gave no further details of the long - term contract . - - Washington Commodities Desk ( 202 ) 898 - 8489 
